comments.body:
Tested locally with the following logic:
```
let mut hash = Sha256::new();
hash.input(b"BIPSchnorr");
let schnorr = hash.finalize();
let mut hash = Sha256::new();
hash.input(&schnorr);
hash.input(&schnorr);
hash.process_current_block();
for i in &hash.hash {
    println!("0x{:08x}", i);
}
```

ACK on the resulting midstate
```
0x048d9a59
0xfe39fb05
0x28479648
0xe4a660f9
0x814b9e66
0x0469e801
0x83909280
0xb329e454
```

