comments.body:
`pubkey_load` uses `ARG_CHECK` in the same way to fire an illegal callback if a zeroed pubkey is used.
```
/* don't check return value */
do_something_with_keypair_that_fails(keypair);
/* keypair is zeroed, ARG_CHECK fails */
do_something_with_secret_part_of_keypair_that_fails(keypair);
```

